{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Adding a GeoJSON file to the map","type":"heading","anchor":"Adding-a-GeoJSON-file-to-the-map"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"MapLibre iOS offers several ways to work with ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"http:\/\/geojson.org\/"},{"text":" files.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"GeoJSON is a standard file format for representing geographic data.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can host a GeoJSON file or bundle it with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"your application, you can use a GeoJSON file as the basis of an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object. Pass the file’s URL into the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:URL:options:"},{"text":" initializer and add the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"shape source to the map using the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:"},{"text":" method. The URL may","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be a local file URL, an HTTP URL, or an HTTPS URL.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Once you’ve added the GeoJSON file to the map via an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"text":" object,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you can configure the appearance of its data and control what data is visible","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"using ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyleLayer"},{"text":" objects. You can also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"#Extracting-GeoJSON-data-from-the-map"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Converting GeoJSON data into shape objects","type":"heading","anchor":"Converting-GeoJSON-data-into-shape-objects"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you have GeoJSON data in the form of source code (also known as “GeoJSON","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"text”), you can convert it into an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature"},{"text":", or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollectionFeature"},{"text":" object that the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"text":" class understands","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"natively. First, create an "},{"code":"NSData","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" object out of the source code string or file"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"contents, then pass that data object into the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape\/shapeWithData:encoding:error:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method. Finally, you can pass the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resulting shape or feature object into the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:shape:options:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" initializer and add it to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map, or you can use the object and its properties to power non-map-related"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"functionality in your application."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To include multiple shapes in the source, create and pass an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollection","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollectionFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:shape:options:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". Alternatively, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:features:options:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:shapes:options:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method to create a shape source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with an array. "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:features:options:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" accepts only "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances, such as "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects, whose attributes you can use when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"applying a predicate to "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or configuring a style layer’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"appearance."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Extracting GeoJSON data from the map","type":"heading","anchor":"Extracting-GeoJSON-data-from-the-map"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Any "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollectionFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object has an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape\/geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method that you can use to create a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON source code representation of the object. You can extract a feature"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object from the map using a method such as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/visibleFeaturesAtPoint:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":2,"text":"About GeoJSON deserialization","type":"heading","anchor":"About-GeoJSON-deserialization"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The process of converting GeoJSON text into "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollectionFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects is known as “GeoJSON deserialization”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON geometries, features, and feature collections are known in this SDK as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shapes, features, and shape collection features, respectively."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Each GeoJSON object type corresponds to a type provided by either this SDK or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the Core Location framework:"}]},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"GeoJSON object type","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"SDK type","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"Position","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (longitude, latitude)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (latitude, longitude)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"Point","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"MultiPoint","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"LineString","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"MultiLineString","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"Polygon","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"MultiPolygon","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"GeometryCollection","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollection","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"Feature","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"FeatureCollection","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollectionFeature","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"type":"table"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"code":"Feature","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" object in GeoJSON corresponds to an instance of an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subclass conforming to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. There is a distinct"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"-conforming class for each type of geometry that a GeoJSON feature"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can contain. This allows features to be used as raw shapes where convenient. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, some features can be added to a map view as annotations. Note that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"identifiers and attributes will not be available for feature querying when a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature is used as an annotation."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In contrast to the GeoJSON standard, it is possible for "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" subclasses"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to straddle the antimeridian."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following GeoJSON data types correspond straightforwardly to Foundation data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"types when they occur as feature identifiers or property values:"}]},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"GeoJSON data type","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Objective-C representation","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift representation","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"null","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSNull","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSNull","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSNumber.boolValue","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"Bool","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Integer","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSNumber.unsignedLongLongValue","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber.longLongValue","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"UInt64","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"Int64","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Floating-point number","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSNumber.doubleValue","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"Double","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"String","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSString","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"String","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"type":"table"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"]]},"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"Working with GeoJSON Data","roleHeading":"Article"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/geojson"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/o